    .prose.max-w-none
      h2.text-2xl.font-semibold.mb-4 Terms of Service
      p.text-gray-700.mb-4
        | By using this application, you agree to comply with all applicable laws and regulations. 
        | This service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.
      
      h3.text-xl.font-semibold.mb-3.text-gray-800 Usage Guidelines
      ul.list-disc.list-inside.text-gray-700.mb-6.space-y-2
        li Use the application responsibly and in accordance with its intended purpose
        li Do not attempt to gain unauthorized access to the system
        li Respect the privacy and rights of other users
        li Report any security vulnerabilities or issues immediately
      
      h2.text-2xl.font-semibold.mb-4.mt-8 Privacy Policy
      p.text-gray-700.mb-4
        | We collect and process your information as follows:
      
      h3.text-xl.font-semibold.mb-3.text-gray-800 Information We Collect
      ul.list-disc.list-inside.text-gray-700.mb-6.space-y-2
        li Email address and name from your Google OAuth account
        li Session information for authentication purposes
        li Usage data to improve our services
      
