      ul.list-disc.list-inside.text-gray-700.mb-6.space-y-2
        li To provide and maintain the authentication service
        li To communicate with you about your account
        li To improve our application and user experience
        li To comply with legal obligations
      
      h3.text-xl.font-semibold.mb-3.text-gray-800 Data Security
      p.text-gray-700.mb-4
        | We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information 
        | against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
      
      h3.text-xl.font-semibold.mb-3.text-gray-800 Contact
      p.text-gray-700
        | If you have any questions about these terms or privacy policy, 
        | please contact us through the application.
    
